<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Unauthorized Access</title>
</head>
<body>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/52ee0b2ef0.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <%- include("header") -%>

    <style>
        *{
            margin: 0px;
            padding: 0px;
            background-color: black;
        }
        .data{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            
        }
        .msg{
            color: white;
            font-size: 30px;
            font-family: monospace;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: row;
        }
        .logo{
            align-items: center;
            width: 250px;
        }
        .text{
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: relative;
            top: -40px;


            & p{
                font-size: 20px;
                opacity: 0.5;
            }
            & .err-msg{
                font-size: 15px;
        }
    }
        .sol{
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            opacity: 0.4;
            max-width: 500px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-family: monospace;
            position: relative;
            bottom: 10px;
            left: 600px;
            

            & li a{
                text-decoration: none;
                color: #2ffc0f;
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
        

    </style>
    
    <div class="data">
        <div class="msg">
            <div class="logo">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-xmark fa-2xl" style="color: #ff0000;font-size: 250px;"></i>
    
            </div>
            <div class="text" >
                <h1>ERROR 401</h1>
                <p>Unauthorized Access</p>
                <p class="err-msg">Oops!! Looks like You aren't Authorized to Access this Webpage</span>
                
            </div>
        </div>  
        </div>
            <div class="sol">
                
                <ul  >
                    <h4>What you can do?</h4>
                    <li>Make sure you're Following to 
                        <a href="https://github.com/bytemait" target="_blank">
                            B.Y.T.E 
                        </a>
                        on GitHub
                    </li>
                    <li>Already Following?? Try refreshing the homepage and try loging in again </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    
</body>
</html>